---
import "../../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>JHU Dynamics - Xi Lin</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-white text-gray-900">
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16 sm:px-10">
      <a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-900">Back to home</a>
      <p class="mt-6 text-sm font-mono text-blue-600">JHU Terradynamics Lab | Robotics Research Intern</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">Research on Cockroach-Inspired Robot Motion and Obstacle Avoidance</h1>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-4xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
        This project focused on dynamics forecasting and trajectory modeling for cockroach-inspired robots. I fused IMU and force data for posture prediction, analyzed nonlinear motion constraints, and built a C++ and MATLAB simulation-validation pipeline around LSTM-based dynamics modeling.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <img src="/assets/projects/jhu-trajectory-model.png" alt="JHU trajectory model" class="w-full rounded-[28px] border border-gray-200 object-cover bg-gray-50" />
        <section class="rounded-[28px] border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Program Core</h2>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
            <li>LSTM dynamics modeling: fused IMU and force data to predict robot posture, with correlation above 0.87 in internal validation.</li>
            <li>Nonlinear constraint modeling: derived motion constraints from posture, angular velocity, and displacement errors.</li>
            <li>Data and simulation pipeline: expanded trajectory data and built a C++ and MATLAB training-validation workflow.</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {["PyTorch", "MATLAB", "C++", "LSTM", "GMM", "Simulation"].map((item) => (
              <span class="rounded-full border border-gray-300 bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
                {item}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 overflow-hidden rounded-[28px] border border-gray-200 bg-white">
        <img src="/assets/projects/jhu-dynamics-table.png" alt="JHU validation summary" class="w-full object-contain" />
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
